# Color System

## Primary Colors
- Brand Primary: `#00b8f5` (sky_blue_400) — `var(--primary)`
- Primary Strong 2: `#004299` (navy_blue_650) — hyperlinks, CTA buttons
- Primary Weak: `#e0f5fd` (sky_blue_50)
- Primary Medium: `#b1e6fb` (sky_blue_100) — sidebar active state

## Semantic State Colors
- Success Strong: `#21c179` / Weak: `#e3f6ec`
- Warning Strong: `#ff9d00` / Weak: `#fff8e1` (use with 60% opacity for P1 cards)
- Error Strong: `#fd5154` / Weak: `#ffebef` (use with 60% opacity for P0 cards)

## Neutral Colors
- Foreground: `#101010` — `var(--foreground)`
- Muted: `#7e7e7e` — `var(--muted-foreground)`
- Border: `#e0e0e0` — `var(--border)`
- Background: `#ffffff`
- Surface Level 3: `#fafafa`
- Offset Weak: `#f5f9fe` — search bars, input fields, subtle backgrounds
- Sidebar: `#e7f1f8`

## Chart Colors
- Chart 1: `#00b8f5`, Chart 2: `#21c179`, Chart 3: `#ff9d00`, Chart 4: `#fd5154`, Chart 5: `#fed533`

## Icon Colors
- Icon container BG: `#e0f5fd` (Primary Weak) — `bg-[#e0f5fd]`
- Icon body/background: `white` — literal `fill="white"` in SVG
- Icon detail color: `#101010` (Foreground) — ALL icons use this single dark color for strokes & detail fills via `currentColor`
- This applies uniformly to: product icons (Card Machine, Sound Box, EMI, AMC), feature icons (Connect Plus), and sidebar nav icons
- NEVER use `#004299` or `#00b8f5` as icon detail colors — those are for hyperlinks and CTA buttons only

## Rules
- Use semantic color names, not raw hex in documentation
- Opacity via Tailwind `/60` syntax: `bg-[#ffebef]/60`
- Hyperlinks: `#004299`, destructive: `var(--destructive)`
- SVG icons MUST use `currentColor` (not hardcoded hex) — see `design-system-icons.mdc`
